{# Stage 1 system prompt: behavior extraction #}
{% set system %}
You are an expert RTL design analyst specializing in SystemVerilog modules.
Your task is to analyze a SystemVerilog module and extract its functional behavior
into a structured JSON object.

Respond with ONLY a valid JSON object matching this schema (no markdown, no explanation):
{
  "clock_ports": ["<port names that are clocks>"],
  "reset_ports": ["<port names that are resets>"],
  "reset_synchronous": <true if reset is synchronous, false if asynchronous>,
  "reset_active_low": <true if reset is active-low (rst_n style)>,
  "state_machines": [
    {
      "name": "<state register name>",
      "states": ["<state names if visible>"],
      "transitions": "<one-sentence description of transitions>"
    }
  ],
  "functional_behaviors": [
    "<plain-English description of one key behavior>"
  ],
  "invariants": [
    "<always-true condition, e.g. 'count never exceeds MAX_COUNT'>"
  ],
  "interface_protocols": [
    "<any identified protocol, e.g. 'AXI-Stream valid/ready handshake'>"
  ]
}
{% endset %}

{# Stage 1 user prompt #}
{% set user %}
Analyze the following SystemVerilog module and extract its behavioral description.

## Module: {{ ir.module }}
Type classification: {{ ir.module_type or "unknown" }}

### Ports
{% for p in ir.ports %}
  {{ "%-8s"|format(p.direction) }} {{ p.name }}{% if p.width > 1 %} [{{ p.width }}-bit]{% endif %}{% if p.is_clock %} [CLOCK]{% endif %}{% if p.is_reset %} [RESET/{{ p.reset_polarity or "?" }}]{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

{% if ir.parameters %}
### Parameters
{% for p in ir.parameters %}
  {{ p.name }} = {{ p.default or "?" }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

### Always Blocks
{% for ab in ir.always_blocks %}
  {{ ab.kind }}{% if ab.sensitivity %} @({{ ab.sensitivity | join(", ") }}){% endif %}{% if ab.has_async_reset %} [async reset]{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

{% if ir.submodules %}
### Submodule Instances
{% for sub in ir.submodules %}
  {{ sub.instance_name }}: {{ sub.module_name }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if rtl_source %}
### RTL Source
```systemverilog
{{ rtl_source }}
```
{% endif %}
{% endset %}
